OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781552859
OL,3,CCanadian PM pays tribute to general
OL,4,Cwho 'helped forge' NI peace process
OL,6,FCanadian Prime Minister Mark Carney
OL,7,Fhas paid tribute to a general who
OL,8,F"helped forge" Northern Ireland's
OL,9,Fpeace process.
OL,11,FMr Carney was speaking at the
OL,12,Finaugural De Chastelain Public Lecture
OL,13,Fat Trinity College Dublin (TCD) as
OL,14,Fpart of his two-day visit to Ireland.
OL,16,FThe lecture is named after Canadian
OL,17,FGeneral John de Chastelain, who was
OL,18,Fhead of the international body charged
OL,19,Fwith decommissioning paramilitary arms
OL,20,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781552859
OL,3,CCanadian PM pays tribute to general
OL,4,Cwho 'helped forge' NI peace process
OL,6,FHe was present in the university's
OL,7,Fexamination Hall as Mr Carney said it
OL,8,Fwas an "honour" to be speaking under
OL,9,Fthe banner of his name.
OL,11,FMr Carney said: "After a lifetime of
OL,12,Fservice, General John de Chastelain's
OL,13,Fseminal work helped forge and
OL,14,Fimplement the Good Friday Agreement.
OL,16,F"Peace is never guaranteed. It cannot
OL,17,Fsimply be signed into reality.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@OO]sD@QOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781552859
OL,3,CCanadian PM pays tribute to general
OL,4,Cwho 'helped forge' NI peace process
OL,6,F"It is brokered, and built, and
OL,7,Fembodied by brave and compassionate
OL,8,Findividuals like General De
OL,9,FChastelain."
OL,11,FMr Carney said Gen De Chastelain
OL,12,F"imagined better possibilities that
OL,13,Fothers did not see".
OL,15,FHe added: "He was ambitious. He
OL,16,Funderstood the power of connection,
OL,17,Fobligation, and trust.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]tD@AOUuD@SO]wD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781552859
OL,3,CCanadian PM pays tribute to general
OL,4,Cwho 'helped forge' NI peace process
OL,6,F"For us, gathered here to honour his
OL,7,Flegacy, this is our charge: We must
OL,8,Fimagine better possibilities, we must
OL,9,Frecognise the importance of our shared
OL,10,Fworld view and weave webs of
OL,11,Fconnection, obligation, and trust `
OL,12,Facross borders and generations."
OL,14,FReferencing the words of Trinity
OL,15,Falumnus Edmund Burke, Mr Carney added:
OL,16,F"If we can do this, if we build
OL,17,Ftogether and with his ambition, we can
OL,18,Farrive at a future worthy of 'those
OL,19,Fwho are living, those who are dead,
OL,20,Fand those who are to be born'."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@`O]xD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
