PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781552859
OL,3,CCanadian PM pays tribute to general
OL,4,Cwho 'helped forge' NI peace process
OL,6,FMr De Chastelain said it was "always a
OL,7,Fpleasure to hear the prime minister
OL,8,Fspeak".
OL,10,FSpeaking to the Press Association
OL,11,Fafter the lecture, he said it was a
OL,12,F"pleasure" to be at the event.
OL,14,FAsked about the tribute to him, Mr De
OL,15,FChastelain said: "A lot of people were
OL,16,Finvolved, you know ` people keep
OL,17,Fsaying what a wonderful job I did, but
OL,18,FI wasn't alone.
OL,26,@nD@^OUpD@FO]tD@AOUtD@JO]wD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781552859
OL,3,CCanadian PM pays tribute to general
OL,4,Cwho 'helped forge' NI peace process
OL,6,F"There were a number of people ` and
OL,7,Fthe most important people were the
OL,8,Fpeople of Ireland, North and South `
OL,9,FWho wanted more than anything else to
OL,10,Fan end to violence."
OL,12,FHe added: "So, we received a lot of
OL,13,Fhelp, it wasn't as though we were
OL,14,Fstruggling on our own. We were getting
OL,15,Fa lot of help.
OL,17,F"We were getting a lot of hindrance by
OL,18,Fsome people who didn't believe in what
OL,19,Fwe were doing ` but it didn't amount
OL,20,Fto much."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]tD@KOUyD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
