PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781552859
OL,3,CCanadian PM pays tribute to general
OL,4,Cwho 'helped forge' NI peace process
OL,6,FAsked for his assessment of how things
OL,7,Fhave developed since his work, Mr De
OL,8,FChastelain said: "I hope fine. I have
OL,9,Fvery little to do with Ireland now
OL,10,Fbut, as far as I know: politically,
OL,11,Feconomically, internationally; I think
OL,12,Fboth countries are thriving.
OL,14,F"Ireland ` as a whole ` was was a
OL,15,Fwonderful place and they're playing a
OL,16,Fvery important part in the world, so,
OL,17,Fyeah, it's great to go back."
OL,26,@pD@ROUvD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
