CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781552859
OL,3,CCanadian PM pays tribute to general
OL,4,Cwho 'helped forge' NI peace process
OL,6,FAt a later event at Dublin Castle,
OL,7,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin described Mr
OL,8,FDe Chastelain as "truly great
OL,9,FCanadian".
OL,11,FHe said: "General, your dedication to
OL,12,Fpeace and reconciliation helped to
OL,13,Fchange the course of this island's
OL,14,Fhistory.
OL,26,@oD@PrppD@ROUqD@IO]sD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
