PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781552859
OL,3,CCanadian PM pays tribute to general
OL,4,Cwho 'helped forge' NI peace process
OL,6,F"Your determination, your skill for
OL,7,Fnegotiation, patience, and unwavering
OL,8,Fmoral leadership were invaluable, and
OL,9,Four debt to you ` a debt owed by
OL,10,Feveryone who calls this island home `
OL,11,Fis as great today as it was on those
OL,12,Fhistoric days."
